Safety JSO (Job Site Observation)
USUI
Used for supervisor observations. A peer or leader
observes an individual performing specific job tasks
and rates their performance. These ratings and
comments, along with any supporting pictures, are
then entered into the Safety JSO application.

Copilot for Power Apps
This feature allows makers and users
to leverage AI to build apps and bring
natural language to their own apps,
making users more productive. It
includes managing and overseeing AI
agents in apps and directing users to
the highest value tasks with in-app
agents.
Learn more
Streamlined Header and
Navigation
Model-driven apps now have an
updated interface with a simplified
header and navigation layout. This
change reduces visual clutter and
makes it easier for users to find and
access key functions, improving
overall usability and navigation
speed.
Learn more
Smart Paste for Forms
Users can now paste data directly
into forms, with automatic mapping
to the correct fields. This feature
saves time and reduces manual entry
errors, especially when dealing with
repetitive or bulk data input.
Learn more
